summary: Follower ranger you can use from the start
descriptionHtml:
This is a Level 1 Dark elf Follower she can be found  at the sleeping giant in in  riverwood . she will level with you.
Due to not having anyone willing to test her out please do not hesitate to let me know if she possibly has a grey face.Even though i do not have it.
for right Now her body  is CBBE. I  She is wearing  leather armor but if you want her to wear  something else.Just trade it to her.

She is set to essential, her perks is  soft foot, sure foot? and set to not effect stealth meter. She  is  a archer.

why do I not make a mage? often mage /spell cast followers will kill the player with their spells once they level .I find this aspect a turn off.


added a precet for  Anoxea Voxx .

to use it you need enhanced character edit. when in racemenu (character creation) sellect body slot next and  the number one slot. make sure dark elf is  sellected as race

to install just download  go to   my documents then>> my games >>skyrim>> copy the cme file here.. you should see saves and skyrim prefferances  skyrim ini.this 
does not go into your program files at all

Update 
Had an error which  someone alerted me hopefully with  some Lucky the CK hasn't trolled me and it is fixed

seems she was not very stealthy as I had wanted  hopefully this update has fixed her


I do not have anyone to test her so I am relying  on  the community .So  I accept feed back.I do apolagize for any  problems
